Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:21.66,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:17705,21668}Whenever my feelings were hurt,\NI couldn't see anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:25.58,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:21668,25588}because I held a lie in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:29.55,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25588,29551}Time moved faster than I could react,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:34.59,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29551,34597}so I pulled myself away\Nfrom everything, but now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:40.64,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:34597,40645}I can't stop anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:47.61,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:41062,47610}Accepting everything, I rise up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:53.49,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:49571,53491}I'll fly over all of time\Nwhile holding onto your presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.99,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:53491,56995}following the trace of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:01:03.00,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56995,63001}My world becomes engulfed with light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:09.25,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:65461,69257}A never ending sky,\Nyour never changing eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:12.96,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:69257,72969}I want to love these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:19.35,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:72969,79350}No matter the distance,\Nor if we are separated
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:22.77,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:79350,82770}we are always connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.44,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:87066,89444}Want you here tonight!
Comment: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:31.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:91112,91112}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.15,0:01:39.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:96159,99662}I heard that Graham's comet\Nwill soon be visible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:41.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:99662,101789}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:44.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:101789,104834}I know Halley's comet,\Nbut not this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:49.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:104834,109172}It's the comet that passes\Nclose to Earth every 50 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:51.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110465,111591}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:56.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:112008,116054}I'm sure it's this Thursday\Nwhen it'll pass by Earth again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:02:00.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116638,120058}How wonderful!\NThis Thursday, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:03.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:120058,123019}How romantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:11.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125647,131235}But you can't see it with the naked\Neye. You have to go to an observatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.23,0:02:16.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:131235,136282}What would happen\Nif a comet crashed into Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:18.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136282,138951}I guess we'd all be blown to bits.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:23.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138951,143748}– Then what will you do, Ryoko?\N– Get my important things and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:26.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:143748,146334}– To where?\N– Your important things?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:30.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:146334,150046}– Let me think…\N– Important things, she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:34.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150046,154092}– My parents, for sure!\N– Mine's my favorite fishing pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:38.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154092,158388}My pillow! I can't sleep without it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:46.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161516,166854}– You guys are a lost cause.\N– What about you, Sawatari?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:50.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168189,170108}Let's run to the end of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:57.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175446,177782}No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:04.74,saint tail default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:180535,184747}A Comet Approaches!\NThe Earth's Final Night!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:06.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185289,186791}You're all idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:11.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186791,191212}A comet never leaves its orbit,\Nso it'll never crash into Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:15.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191963,195967}I said "suppose"!\NDon't call me an idiot, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:18.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195967,198094}You want a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:23.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198094,203391}So that's it! You don't have anything\Nimportant to take, so you're mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:27.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203975,207645}What? You're wrong!\NI do too have something precious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:31.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:208229,211274}– Then tell us!\N– You really want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:36.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211274,216112}Are you two friends or enemies?\NMake up your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:44.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220742,224829}– Who wants to be friends with him?\N– Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:02.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238050,242138}{\i1}He didn't have time to tell me\Nwhat his important thing was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:05.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243890,245808}{\i1}Time to make up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:08.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245808,248686}{\i1}I'm not in love with her or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250104,251731}{\i1}I just don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:17.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255818,257945}I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:22.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258196,262450}{\i1}We must let the American people\Nknow to prevent a tragedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:25.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262700,265912}{\i1}But that will only cause a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:29.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:266370,269874}{\i1}– You're saying to keep quiet?\N– We only have a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:31.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270500,271876}I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:35.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272710,275338}Oh, welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:37.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275880,277423}{\i1}It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:40.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277423,280218}{\i1}It's too soon to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:44.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280218,284639}– Mom, where's my snack?\N– There should be something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:46.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284639,286516}Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:51.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286516,291646}Gosh! What are they watching anyway,\Nall cuddled up during the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:57.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293731,297527}"Comet collides!\NThe last night on Earth"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:15.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313084,315336}It brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:19.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:315336,319966}It sure did. This was the movie\Nwe saw on our first date.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:22.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:320842,322969}Genichiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:25.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323970,325972}Eimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:33.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331143,333938}I guess I'll go change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:37.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334856,337859}{\i1}This is so embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:45.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:343573,345908}Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:49.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347785,349412}What is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:53.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349579,353249}Well, it's an incident that\Noccurred about an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:56.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:354500,356961}I'm first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356961,358713}Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:00.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358713,360756}You mustn't run around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:03.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361382,363259}I'm sorry, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:08.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363926,368723}You're in the choir, aren't you?\NWhat's the big hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:09.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368723,369724}Truth is…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:15.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373269,375187}Graham's comet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:19.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375688,379734}That's right, Sister.\NWe have to see that comet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:22.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379734,382028}Akio's going to move away soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:26.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382028,386157}That's why we all decided\Nto go see the comet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:28.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386532,388409}You can't see it with your naked eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:29.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388701,389952}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:36.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389952,396167}So I went to the observatory and asked\Nif we could use the telescope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:38.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396167,398836}At first they agreed, but then…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:44.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401297,404300}No one's told me\Nanything about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:47.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404759,407595}But I talked to\Nthe director last week!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:49.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:407595,409847}Last week?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:52.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409847,412516}That director was transferred\Nto another observatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:54.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412975,414185}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:57.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414185,417021}Then let us talk to the new director!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:07:01.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417563,421525}He's a busy man.\NYou're disrupting our work. Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:02.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421901,422777}Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:03.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422777,423778}It's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:09.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423778,429450}We were looking forward to it.\NSo we came to pray for God's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:12.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429700,432203}So we can get to see the comet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:20.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437750,440795}Isn't there some other way, Seira?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:25.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440795,445466}You can only see it with an\Nobservatory's astronomical telescope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:28.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:445967,448260}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:32.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:448260,452181}Okay! Let St. Tail handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:42.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457895,462358}It looks like that Sawatari's\Nreally serious about Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:47.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462358,467697}I wonder what got into him. He was\Nnever interested in girls before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:50.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:467697,470950}– What do you think, Asuka?\N– How would I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:53.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471784,473160}What a grouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:57.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474203,477123}– Who cares?\N– Hey! The enemy is approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:08:00.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477623,480126}Prepare to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:03.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482420,483963}What…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:06.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483963,486590}What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:18.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493472,498477}Rotten kids! How dare you\Nattack an innocent passerby?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:23.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500855,503190}Adults are all liars!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:34.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511115,514452}Hey, Asuka, looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:36.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:514452,516454}You can't hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:40.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518414,520249}Great strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:48.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526756,528424}"Dear Mr. Detective:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:53.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528424,533971}I will steal Graham's comet\Nthis coming Thursday. – St. Tail"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:57.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534764,537725}– It's a challenge!\N– A challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:09:00.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537725,540561}Wow! Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:03.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540561,543189}How's she gonna steal a comet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:05.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543189,545024}There's no way…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:07.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545733,547735}Wait! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:12.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547735,552156}She's gonna steal\Nthe observatory's telescope!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:15.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552156,555868}That's the only way to see\Nthe comet around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:20.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557787,560998}My theory's definitely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:23.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560998,563375}Never mind.\NYou're dripping all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:26.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564293,566879}But stealing it won't be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:28.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566879,568964}I also agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:30.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568964,570341}Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:35.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:571509,575471}She'll think of a way!\NI'll be ready for you, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:38.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575471,578641}How can he be so sure\Nbased on no facts?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:41.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578641,581727}I don't know.\NIt must be love, love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:48.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585314,588776}It's a perfect night to present\Nthe comet to the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:51.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589610,591779}Ruby, take care of things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:58.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596408,598494}No, Ruby! I have work to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:04.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601413,604416}Oh, all right. Will you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:08.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606001,608295}Okay. But just this one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:16.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612800,616470}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:22.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621559,622476}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:26.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625062,626147}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:30.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628274,630401}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:52.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:647710,652423}Meimi, hurry! Everyone will be\Nhere soon for choir practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:56.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653382,656385}I know. You and Ruby take care\Nof the other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:59.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656760,659346}The children will be happy for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:02.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660806,662641}You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:08.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664977,668606}May the blessings of God be with us.
Comment: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:15.69,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:675696,675696}Eyecatch A
Comment: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:21.70,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:681702,681702}Eyecatch B
Comment: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:26.70,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:686707,686707}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:47.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703390,707394}{\i1}Wow. This certainly is\Na magnificent telescope.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:53.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:712900,713859}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:57.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714151,717196}But why does she want a telescope?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:02.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:718489,722117}It will go smoothly tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:03.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:722117,723827}Especially without those pesky kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:08.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724703,728624}We can't let those kids ruin\Nsuch a great astronomical event.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:13.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:728624,733295}– How's it going?\N– Everything's going smoothly, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:14.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:733587,734755}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:19.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734755,739760}Asuka Jr., is St. Tail really\Ncoming to steal this telescope?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:21.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:740219,741762}I'm certain of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:25.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:742304,745599}{\i1}You've got the right idea\Nexcept for the last detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:30.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:746558,750020}We'll leave you\Nto take care of St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:33.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750020,753190}We don't want our research\Nhampered by a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:35.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:753816,755609}{\i1}Of all the nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:40.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755609,760447}{\i1}The comet passes once every 50 years.\NIt's just as important to children.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:45.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:760447,765160}{\i1}They want to keep it for themselves.\NGod will never forgive this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:46.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765619,766662}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:49.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768414,769999}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:51.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770165,771417}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:13:01.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778507,781176}– Where did they come from?\N– Who did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:03.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781176,783554}Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:07.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786098,787683}Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:13.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:791270,793022}I know it's you, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:20.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:797067,800446}{\i1}How's she gonna steal\Nthis huge thing anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:35.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812791,815377}Well, that's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:40.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815377,820883}And now, I have some sad news\Nfor all of you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:46.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821425,826847}Today is Akio's last practice,\Nsince he will be leaving soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:54.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833145,834855}– Take care.\N– Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:57.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835731,837775}Too bad we couldn't see the comet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:13:59.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837775,839151}It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:00.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839151,840778}See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:06.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841695,846575}Akio, I hope you never lose\Nyour bright outlook on life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:09.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:846575,849536}I won't! Goodbye, Mother Superior!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:10.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849536,850371}Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:17.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854458,857795}Mother Superior, where is Seira?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:19.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857795,859338}She's not out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:27.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:865135,867805}Oh, but I am outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:33.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:870015,873018}Though this is a little embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:40.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:875354,880484}Hello, children! These balloons\Nare for you from the snowman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:45.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883195,885739}This is a reward for being so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:48.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885739,888367}Gee, thanks, Mr. Snowman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:52.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888992,892830}There's one for everyone.\NHere you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:54.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893205,894790}Wow! A snowman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:14:59.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898001,899294}Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:01.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899628,901296}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:14.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:909763,914184}Hey, Akio. There's something\Non your balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:21.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:918105,921650}"Come to the observatory.\NI'll give you Graham's comet."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:24.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922985,924403}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:26.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924403,926071}Where are you kids going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:28.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926530,928574}We'll be right back, Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:34.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:932995,934079}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:36.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934079,936081}Get down here, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:38.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936081,938542}If you don't, I'm going up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:44.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941044,944006}I'll get you for sure today\Nand unmask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:53.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951513,953223}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:57.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:954183,957102}Show…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:16:00.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958020,960314}Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:11.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968780,971992}Sir! This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:15.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972743,975037}Look at the monitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:16.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975037,976205}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:19.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976205,979500}A part of the comet has broken off
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:22.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979500,982252}and is falling towards us\Nat great speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:24.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:982252,984796}That's ridiculous! Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:29.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:985881,989384}Why didn't you see this before?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:30.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989384,990552}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:36.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:991303,996141}A part of the comet.\NThat's something like a meteor, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:38.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996141,998143}No, very far from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:42.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998143,1002523}It could make a huge hole!\NWe may not be safe here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:46.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002523,1006944}– Let's get away!\N– Wait for me! Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:50.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007361,1010447}{\i1}Everyone's gone finally!\NNow's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:53.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010447,1013659}Hey, you!\NDon't you move from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:17:01.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016537,1021583}Why aren't you running away?\NA part of the comet is heading here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:03.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022459,1023961}So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:07.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023961,1027548}So what? What could you\Nbe thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:09.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028257,1029800}I'm gonna arrest you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:17.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035055,1037766}{\i1}My legs, I can't move them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:20.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038934,1040435}Is there another reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:24.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040894,1044898}Like what if you died, what's\Nthe most important thing you'd take?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:26.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045566,1046900}Something important?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:29.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047651,1049695}Yes. Do you have something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:30.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049695,1050529}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:34.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050529,1054324}I can't think of anything\Nuntil I arrest you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:53.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071133,1073969}{\i1}Meimi, no! Get ahold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:06.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085105,1086898}I'm sorry. It was an act.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:12.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087441,1092362}Nothing's falling to Earth.\NI rigged the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:14.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093071,1094364}You what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:17.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094698,1097868}One! Two! Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:27.33,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1106376,1107336}{\an2}Comet Collides!\NThe Last Night On Earth – The End
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:29.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107669,1109838}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:45.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122851,1125228}Hey! Why did you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:51.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127481,1131693}Don't worry. I've recorded\Nthe correct data too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:55.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131693,1135656}And could you let in\Nthe children waiting outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136031,1137616}Outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:00.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138867,1140661}Rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:02.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140869,1142913}Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:07.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145624,1147542}Boy, that was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:14.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1148335,1154341}But if he knew I was Meimi,\NI'm sure he wouldn't have said it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:23.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161431,1163809}The children waiting outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:39.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177030,1179074}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:47.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184579,1187040}Wow, there it is! I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:49.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187290,1189835}– The comet!\N– It really has a tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:51.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189835,1191670}Yeah, this is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:57.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193296,1197509}– I wonder when we'll see it again?\N– In 50 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:20:00.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197509,1200887}Then let's all come here\Nagain to look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:02.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200887,1202139}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:05.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202139,1205350}I just don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:10.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205350,1210021}Why did St. Tail do this?\NHey, what's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:13.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210021,1213650}Thank you, sir.\NWe all prayed to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:17.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214401,1217404}We asked Him\Nto let us see the comet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:22.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219531,1222075}Thank you, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:25.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222826,1225036}God, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:30.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1226580,1230751}Look, falling stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:37.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234463,1237507}Did you ask God for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:41.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239009,1241219}– No.\N– Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:45.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242053,1245140}{\i1}Because my wish…
